Project ME

Elements of an Autobiography
-Written in FIRST person
-Serrings and events are described very vividly(use five sences)
-Includes enecdotes(stories)
-Written in chronological order

Why write an Autobiography?

-Learning about ourselves 
 Gives us purpose in life

Project Me will essentually be your
own autobiography. It will take the
entire school year to write, but we
will write it one chapter at a timie
from now until then.

Chapter 1
WHO AM I?
due AUGUST 31st

This chapter highlights who you are right now.
-When is your birthday
-Where where you born
-Where do you fit in your family?
-What color is your hair eye's etc.

